{
  "stem": "25114.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the other place we went to, we found the fires burning and the butts of cigarettes still alight from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So these 50 people who stayed behind-- so I was among them and my husband.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were playing-- only because those were the people who knew every tree of that forest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- we were playing with the Germans, cat and mouse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came in where we were, we came where they were before, and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But somehow we escaped them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody got hurt, but it was very close.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And eventually the siege-- it went to the-- to the places which got burnt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's a lot of things were still on the fields, like potatoes, and vegetables, and honey, and runaway chicken and pigs and things, you know, because they couldn't burn everything in-- as they're taking away the peasants.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we eventually the siege ended, and we started gathering all that stuff from the fields.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We started getting potatoes and bringing in all the useful things, items from the burned-out houses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, you know, the windows and the doors, and also the stoves, and-- and other things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for-- for a little while, you know, I got very ill because after all this-- after all this I got very ill.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a weak stomach condition, I had big ulcer on my breast, and altogether, you know, I was very-- very sick.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was walking with a stick, and very-- decimated, you know, and everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the doctor examined me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, can't hear the heartbeat of the baby, and he can't cure my breast ulcer because I was-- has no medication.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And anyway, we'll see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this time was peaceful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had made some tents-- not tents.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
